The paper discusses the interplay between NOMA and various wireless technologies such as MIMO, millimeter wave communications, cognitive and cooperative communications, visible light communications, physical layer security, energy harvesting, and wireless caching. These technologies are all related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), communication and security (cs.COMM), systems and control (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.COMM, cs.SY, and cs.MM, in that order.
